#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events.rst:63
msgid ""
"By default, the :guilabel:`Events` dashboard is displayed in the :icon:`oi-"
"view-kanban` :guilabel:`Kanban` view, which is populated with a variety of "
"pipeline stages."
