"allowed to execute this rule. Leave the field empty to allow all groups. See "
"this documentation: :ref:`access-rights/groups`."
msgstr ""
"在\\ :guilabel:`要執行的動作`\\ 分頁下，選擇\\ :guilabel:`加入動作`\\ 。接著"
"，在出現的\\ :guilabel:`建立動作`\\ 彈出視窗中，選擇\\ :guilabel:`傳送短訊`\\"
" ，並設定\\ :guilabel:`允許的群組`\\ 。\\ :guilabel:`允許的群組`\\ 是允許執行"
"此規則的存取權限群組。將此欄位留空可允許所有群組。請參閱此使用說明：\\ "
":ref:`access-rights/groups`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_analysis.rst:84
msgid ""
"Next, set the :guilabel:`SMS Template` and choose whether the SMS message "
"should be logged as a note, by making a selection in the drop-down "
"menu: :guilabel:`Send SMS as`. Click :guilabel:`Save and Close` to save the "
"changes to this new action."
msgstr ""
"接下來，設定\\ :guilabel:`短訊範本`\\ 並選擇是否將短訊記錄為備註，方法是在下"
"拉式選單中選取：\\ :guilabel:`傳送短訊為`\\ 。按一下\\ :guilabel:`儲存並關"
"閉`\\ 以儲存此新動作的變更。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_analysis.rst:None
msgid ""
"Automation rule template with rule to do, SMS template and log as note "
"highlighted."
msgstr "自動化規則範本，其中強調要執行的規則、短訊範本和記錄為備註。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_analysis.rst:92
msgid ""
"Add any necessary notes under the :guilabel:`Notes` tab. Finally, navigate "
"away from the completed automation rule, or manually save (by clicking "
"the :guilabel:`☁️ (cloud)` icon), to implement the change."
msgstr ""
"在\\ :guilabel:`備註`\\ 分頁下加入任何必要的備註。最後，離開已完成的自動化規"
"則，或手動儲存（按一下\\ :guilabel:`☁️（雲端）`\\ 圖示），以實施變更。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:3
msgid "SMS via Twilio"
msgstr "透過 Twilio 傳送短訊"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:6
msgid "What is Twilio"
msgstr "什麼是 Twilio"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:8
msgid ""
"Twilio is a third-party provider that enables you to send SMS messages to "
"your clients. Odoo provides an easy way to use this service within your Odoo "
"apps."
msgstr ""
"Twilio 是第三方供應商，可讓您向客戶傳送短訊。Odoo 提供在您的 Odoo 應用程式中"
"使用此服務的簡便方式。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:12
msgid "Why would I need it?"
msgstr "為什麼需要它？"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:14
msgid ""
"Although Odoo already comes with an out-of-the-box (IAP) solution for SMS "
"messages, it might not work in some countries with stricter legal "
"requirements. Currently, Odoo registers itself when possible to avoid extra "
"setup for its customers, however in some countries that is not enough and "
"the client itself must do it. This can be done through Twilio."
msgstr ""
"雖然 Odoo 已經內建（IAP）短訊解決方案，但在某些法律要求較嚴格的國家/地區可能"
"無法運作。目前，Odoo 會在可能的情況下自行註冊，以避免客戶需要額外設定，但在某"
"些國家/地區這樣並不夠，客戶本身必須進行註冊。這可以透過 Twilio 完成。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:20
msgid "Setup your Twilio account"
msgstr "設定您的 Twilio 帳戶"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:22
msgid ""
"By creating a Twilio account, you will be able to create a virtual phone "
"number from which you will be able to send SMS messages. These cost credits "
"that are to be bought on Twilio, not Odoo."
msgstr ""
"建立 Twilio 帳戶後，您將能夠建立虛擬電話號碼，從中傳送短訊。這些需要在 "
"Twilio 而非 Odoo 上購買點數。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:25
msgid "Go to `Twilio <https://www.twilio.com>`_"
msgstr "前往 `Twilio <https://www.twilio.com>`_"

